{"tid":769029,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"疑借盧凱彤離世發財　網民嬲爆齊插無恥","createTime":"2018-08-06T01:32:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T02:03:49.000Z","uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0393176d1063282ea4c7efe0a2dcfa9a7e00ee3c","tid":769029,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T01:32:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180806/mobile/bkn-20180806032122065-0806_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20180806%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180806032122065-0806_00862_001.html&d=POMUm6bgrTSZDVo5mNZtoZzN29kXmk9bB7xBuKM86BA%3D&h=d6836960\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20180806/mobile/bkn-20180806032122065-0806_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n受躁鬱症影響的歌手盧凱彤（Ellen）昨日突然在跑馬地寓所自殺墮斃，事件震驚全城，網民紛紛留言表示哀痛，但係竟然有公司疑借呢件事做宣傳，有發死人財之嫌！ <br />\n<br />\n有一間瑜伽公司喺社交網專頁發文，指Ellen離世事件感到意外同令人惋惜，話身心健康好重要，特別係遇到困難時要學識處理，就算依家冇問題，都應該要學定去預防，甚至介紹畀身邊有需要嘅朋友，跟住就列出一啲課程，有晒上堂時間同埋收費！唔少網民睇到呢度即時發火，覺得呢間公司消費死人好冇道德狂插佢哋無恥，有網民以食花生心態留言話想睇吓呢次「關公災難」點收科。"},{"pid":"26304abcf3c65d2d3b224994e91807bd1d45c52f","tid":769029,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T01:59:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"952fddecc9fbe850bf98f36b0fb6233fadc9bb9d","tid":769029,"uid":5499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T02:02:14.000Z","msg":"過2日就唔記得啦，關咩公災難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc8bfc20995485c8eef06ee8b43d062040a9fcde","tid":769029,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T02:03:49.000Z","msg":"香港人有咩資格講公關？<br />\n福喜事件你地仲記得？<br />\n港鐵上至ceo下至查飛狗都無公關嫁啦，咪日日爆日日賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}